org.rocketproplab.marginalstability.flightcomputer

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rocketproplab.marginalstability.flightcomputer.Settings

  • public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
    The settings class contains constants that will be loaded form disk on startup. All constant values that might need to change in a debugging session should be put here.
